OL,3,CSpeaker still under pressure as almost
OL,4,C70 MPs sign call for him to quit
OL,6,FSir Lindsay Hoyle is facing continued
OL,7,Fpressure to step down as Commons
OL,8,FSpeaker after almost 70 MPs called for
OL,9,Fhim to go.
OL,11,FSome 67 MPs, more than a tenth of the
OL,12,FCommons, have signed a motion proposed
OL,13,Fby senior Conservative William Wragg
OL,14,Fexpressing no confidence in the
OL,15,FSpeaker over his handling of the Gaza
OL,16,Fceasefire debate on Wednesday.
OL,18,FSir Lindsay has apologised for his
OL,19,Fhandling of the debate and offered an
OL,20,Femergency debate on the SNP's motion
OL,21,Fcalling for a ceasefire.
