OL,6,FBut criticism from SNP and Tory MPs
OL,7,Fhas continued, with the Prime Minister
OL,8,Fdescribing his decisions as "very
OL,9,Fconcerning".
OL,11,FIf further signatures are added to Mr
OL,12,FWragg's motion, Sir Lindsey will face
OL,13,Fadditional pressure to go.
OL,15,FThere is no formal procedure for
OL,16,Fremoving a speaker, but in 2009
OL,17,FMichael Martin resigned from the post
OL,18,Fafter it became clear he had lost the
OL,19,Fconfidence of MPs across the Commons.
