OL,6,FSir Lindsay's explanation that he was
OL,7,Fmotivated by concern about MPs'
OL,8,Fsecurity has sparked further debate
OL,9,Fabout the impact of threats and
OL,10,Fintimidation around the work of
OL,11,FParliament.
OL,13,FRishi Sunak said on Thursday:
OL,14,F"Parliament is an important place for
OL,15,Fus to have these debates. And just
OL,16,Fbecause some people may want to stifle
OL,17,Fthat with intimidation or aggressive
OL,18,Fbehaviour, we should not bend to that
OL,19,Fand change how Parliament works.
OL,21,F"That's a very slippery slope."
