OL,9,FSir Keir Starmer.
OL,11,FMs Braverman said the Labour leader
OL,12,Fhad "bowed to the mob" and made a
OL,13,F"grubby backroom deal".
OL,15,FShe said: "The mask has slipped: in
OL,16,Fhock to the Islamists, he is
OL,17,Fresponsible for one of the most
OL,18,Fshameful days of our democracy.
